Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:14.85,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}私たちはいつでも
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.98,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,100)\blur3}勘違いだとか
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.32,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}自信で生きてる
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:31.53,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}大事な宝物ね
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:34.66,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}しまえるように
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:37.89,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}こころ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.66,0:01:43.55,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}きっと見えなくなってるよ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.72,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}ぐるぐる回せ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.51,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}この魔法の杖で
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:52.64,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}涙とSunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.10,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}混ぜたら
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.19,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂しがりやさん
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.73,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}夢はかなうよ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.44,OPJ,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}いつだって
