Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.04,0:00:59.25,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}那个时候的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.44,0:01:03.01,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}戴着无法飞翔的螺旋桨
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.55,0:01:06.97,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}抬头仰望着半分天空
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.01,0:01:10.47,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}一路赤脚追逐着
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.22,0:01:14.85,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}始终如此的我们
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.27,0:01:17.98,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}也许一直在误解
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.27,0:01:21.32,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,50)\blur3}持有自信迎面生活
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.86,0:01:31.53,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}重要的宝物
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.87,0:01:34.66,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}为了能够永久珍藏
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.95,0:01:43.55,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\blur3}这份心情  一定会消失不见
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.59,0:01:46.72,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}旋转起来吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.80,0:01:49.51,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}持有着这魔法之仗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:52.64,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}眼泪与Sunny day
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.85,0:01:55.10,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,200)\blur3}溶于心中
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.60,0:01:59.19,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}寂寞的人的身旁
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.90,0:02:01.73,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(50,100)\blur3}会有梦想绽放
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.98,0:02:04.44,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}不管何时
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:07.70,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}伴随左右
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.07,0:02:12.20,OPC,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,200)\blur3}我们一起
